  }}}}'''柚皮素'''是一种无味，颜色由白色至淡黄的[[黄烷酮|黄烷酮]]，是一种[[黄酮类化合物|类黄酮]]。它是[[葡萄柚|葡萄柚中]]的主要黄烷酮，<ref name="pmid11093936">{{Cite journal|title=Bioavailability of the flavanone naringenin and its glycosides in rats|url=https://hal.inrae.fr/hal-02694848/file/67273_20100906040812887_1.pdf|date=December 2000|journal=Am. J. Physiol. Gastrointest. Liver Physiol.|issue=6|doi=10.1152/ajpgi.2000.279.6.G1148|volume=279|pages=G1148–54|pmid=11093936|access-date=2020-09-29|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107180119/https://hal.inrae.fr/hal-02694848/file/67273_20100906040812887_1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>并存在于多种水果与草药中。 <ref name="Yáñez 159–181">{{Cite journal|title=Methods of analysis and separation of chiral flavonoids|last=Yáñez|first=Jaime A.|last2=Andrews|first2=Preston K.|date=2007-04-01|journal=Journal of Chromatography B|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.jchromb.2006.10.052|volume=848|pages=159–181|pmid=17113835|last3=Davies|first3=Neal M.}}</ref>

== 结构 ==
柚皮素具有黄烷酮的骨架结构，其4'，5和7位碳原子处有三个[[羟基|羟基]]。柚皮素可以单体存在，亦有[[糖苷|糖苷]]形式即[[柚皮苷|柚皮苷]]，其具有加入的[[二糖|二糖]][[新橙皮苷|新橙皮糖]]与7位碳原子连接而成。

像大多数黄烷酮一样，柚皮素在碳2上有一个手性中心，尽管光学纯度是可变的。 <ref name="Yáñez 159–181">{{Cite journal|title=Methods of analysis and separation of chiral flavonoids|last=Yáñez|first=Jaime A.|last2=Andrews|first2=Preston K.|date=2007-04-01|journal=Journal of Chromatography B|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.jchromb.2006.10.052|volume=848|pages=159–181|pmid=17113835|last3=Davies|first3=Neal M.}}</ref> <ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Pharmacokinetics of selected chiral flavonoids: hesperetin, naringenin and eriodictyol in rats and their content in fruit juices|last=Yáñez|first=Jaime A.|last2=Remsberg|first2=Connie M.|date=2008-01-01|journal=Biopharmaceutics & Drug Disposition|issue=2|doi=10.1002/bdd.588|volume=29|pages=63–82|language=en|issn=1099-081X|pmid=18058792|last3=Miranda|first3=Nicole D.|last4=Vega-Villa|first4=Karina R.|last5=Andrews|first5=Preston K.|last6=Davies|first6=Neal M.}}</ref> S(-)-柚皮素的[[消旋|外消旋]]已显示相当快地发生。 <ref name="Krause 69–72">{{Cite journal|title=Analysis of enantiomeric flavanones in plant extracts by high-performance liquid chromatography on a cellulose triacetate based chiral stationary phase|last=Krause|first=M.|last2=Galensa|first2=R.|date=1991-07-01|journal=Chromatographia|issue=1–2|doi=10.1007/BF02262470|volume=32|pages=69–72|language=en|issn=0009-5893}}</ref>

== 来源和生物利用度 ==
