irst9=G. P.}}</ref> <ref name="#1">{{Cite journal|title=Changes in the polyphenol profile of tomato juices processed by pulsed electric fields|url=|last=Vallverdú-Queralt|first=A|last2=Odriozola-Serrano|first2=I|journal=J Agric Food Chem|issue=38|doi=10.1021/jf302791k|year=2012|volume=60|pages=9667–9672|pmid=22957841|last3=Oms-Oliu|first3=G|last4=Lamuela-Raventós|first4=RM|last5=Elez-Martínez|first5=P|last6=Martín-Belloso|first6=O|authorlink6=Olga Martín-Belloso}}</ref>[[可可豆|可可]]，<ref name="#2">{{Cite journal|title=Liquid chromatographic/electrospray ionization tandem mass spectrometric study of the phenolic composition of cocoa (Theobroma cacao)|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-mass-spectrometry_2003-01_38_1/page/35|last=Sánchez-Rabaneda|first=Ferran|last2=Jáuregui|first2=Olga|date=2003-01-01|journal=Journal of Mass Spectrometry|issue=1|doi=10.1002/jms.395|volume=38|pages=35–42|bibcode=2003JMSp...38...35S|issn=1076-5174|pmid=12526004|last3=Casals|first3=Isidre|last4=Andrés-Lacueva|first4=Cristina|last5=Izquierdo-Pulido|first5=Maria|last6=Lamuela-Raventós|first6=Rosa M.}}</ref> <ref name="#1"/> <ref name="#2"/>[[丹参|希腊牛至]]，<ref>{{Cite journal|title=LC-UV-Solid-Phase Extraction-NMR-MS Combined with a Cryogenic Flow Probe and Its Application to the Identification of Compounds Present in Greek Oregano|last=Exarchou|first=Vassiliki|last2=Godejohann|first2=Markus|date=2003-11-01|journal=Analytical Chemistry|issue=22|doi=10.1021/ac0347819|volume=75|pages=6288–6294|issn=0003-2700|pmid=14616013|last3=van Beek|first3=Teris A.|last4=Gerothanassis|first4=Ioannis P.|last5=Vervoort|first5=Jacques}}</ref>[[水薄荷|水薄荷]]，<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Isolation of the MAO-inhibitor naringenin from Mentha aquatica L.|last=Olsen|first=Helle T.|last2=Stafford|first2=Gary I.|date=2008-05-22|journal=Journal of Ethnopharmacology|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.jep.2008.02.015|volume=117|pages=500–502|pmid=18372132|last3=van Staden|first3=Johannes|last4=Christensen|first4=Søren B.|last5=Jäger|first5=Anna K.}}</ref>以及[[豆类|豆类]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Effects of flavonoids released naturally from bean (Phaseolus vulgaris) on nodD-regulated gene transcription in Rhizobium leguminosarum bv. phaseoli|last=Hungria|first=M.|last2=Johnston|first2=A. W.|date=1992-05-01|journal=Molecular Plant-Microbe Interactions|issue=3|doi=10.1094/mpmi-5-199|volume=5|pages=199–203|issn=0894-0282|pmid=1421508|last3=Phillips|first3=D. A.}}</ref>柚皮素与柚皮苷的比例因来源而异，对映体比例也是如此。 <ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=Pharmacokinetics of selected chiral flavonoids: hesperetin, naringenin and eriodictyol in rats and their content in fruit juices|last=Yáñez|first=Jaime A.|last2=Remsberg|first2=Connie M.|date=2008-01-01|journal=Biopharmaceutics & Drug Disposition|issue=2|doi=10.1002/bdd.588|volume=29|pages=63–82|language=en|issn=1099-081X|pmid=18058792|last3=Miranda|first3=Nicole D.|last4=Vega-Villa|first4=Karina R.|last5=Andrews|first5=Preston K.|last6=Davies|first6=Neal M.}}</ref>

[[柚皮苷7-葡萄糖苷|柚皮苷-7-葡萄糖苷]]形式的生物利用度似乎低于[[糖苷配基|聚乙二醇]]形式。<ref name="pmid10558881">{{Cite journal|title=Interactions of the flavonoid naringenin in the gastrointestinal tract and the influence of glycosylation|date=November 1999|journal=Biochem. Biophys. Res. Commun.|issue=2|doi=10.1006/bbrc.1999.1695|volume=265|pages=410–5|pmid=10558881}}</ref>

服用葡萄柚汁后，柚皮素血浆浓度比服用橙汁更高。 <ref name="pmid11160539">{{Cite journal|title=Plasma kinetics and urinary excretion of the flavanones naringenin and hesperetin in humans after ingestion of orange juice and grapefruit juice|date=February 2001|journal=J. Nutr.|issue=2|doi=10.1093/jn/131.2.235|volume=131|pages=235–41|pmid=11160539}}</ref>在葡萄柚中还发现了相关的化合物[[山柰酚|山柰酚]]，其[[羟基|羟基]]紧挨着[[酮基|酮基]]。

柚皮素可以从煮熟的番茄酱中吸收。 每10克番茄酱中含有253毫克柚皮素。 <ref name="pmid12421849">{{Cite journal|title=Naringenin from cooked tomato paste is bioavailable in men|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-nutrition_2002-11_132_11/page/3349|date=November 2002|journal=J. Nutr.|issue=11|doi=10.1093/jn/132.11.3349|volume=132|pages=3349–52|pmid=12421849}}</ref>

== 生物合成与代谢 ==
它衍生自[[丙二酰辅酶A|丙二酰基CoA]]和[[香豆酰辅酶A|4-香豆酰基CoA]] 。后者衍生自[[苯丙氨酸|苯丙氨酸]]。将所得[[丁烯酮|丁烯酮]]通过作用于查耳酮合成酶，得到查耳酮。查尔酮随后经历闭环，生成柚皮素。 <ref name="pmid2450022">{{Cite journal|title=Characterization of Stilbene Synthase Genes in Mulberry (''Morus atropurpurea'') and Metabolic Engineering for the Production of Resveratrol in ''Escherichia coli''|last=Wang|first=Chuanhong|last2=Zhi|first2=Shuang|journal=Journal of Agricultural and Food Chemistry|issue=8|doi=10.1021/acs.jafc.6b05212|year=2017|volume=65|pages=1659–1668|pmid=28168876|last3=Liu|first3=Changying|last4=Xu|first4=Fengxiang|last5=Zhao|first5=Aichun|last6=Wang|first6=Xiling|last7=Ren|first7=Yanhong|last8=Li|first8=Zhengang|last9=Yu|first9=Maode}}</ref>

[[柚皮素8-二甲基烯丙基转移酶|柚皮素-8-二甲基烯丙基转移酶]]使用[[焦磷酸二甲基烯丙酯|二甲基烯丙基二磷酸]]和(−)- (2S)''-''柚皮素以产生二磷酸和[[8-异戊烯基柚皮苷|8-戊基柚皮素]] 。[[线虫|雅致小克银汉霉]]（''Cunninghamella elegans''）是一种哺乳动物新陈代谢的真菌模型生物，它可用于研究柚皮素的[[酸硫化|硫酸化]]。 <ref name="pmid10680173">{{Cite journal|title=Sulfation of naringenin by Cunninghamella elegans|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_phytochemistry_2000-01_53_2/page/209|last=Ibrahim AR|date=January 2000|journal=Phytochemistry|issue=2|doi=10.1016/S0031-9422(99)00487-2|volume=53|pages=209–12|pmid=10680173}}</ref>

== 潜在的生物学影响 ==

=== 抗菌，抗真菌和抗病毒 ===
柚皮素对表皮葡萄球菌，[[金黃色葡萄球菌|金黄色葡萄球菌]]，[[枯草桿菌|枯草芽孢杆菌]]，[[黄褐微球菌|黄球菌]]和[[大腸桿菌|大肠杆菌]]具有抗菌作用。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Antimicrobial effects of Finnish plant extracts containing flavonoids and other phenolic compounds|last=Rauha|first=Jussi-Pekka|last2=Remes|first2=Susanna|date=2000-05-25|journal=International Journal of Food Microbiology|issue=1|doi=10.1016/S0168-1605(00)00218-X|volume=56|pages=3–12|pmid=10857921|last3=Heinonen|first3=Marina|last4=Hopia|first4=Anu|last5=Kähkönen|first5=Marja|last6=Kujala|first6=Tytti|last7=Pihlaja|first7=Kalevi|last8=Vuorela|first8=Heikki|last9=Vuorela|first9=Pia}}</ref>进一步的研究增加了对[[乳酸乳球菌|乳酸乳球菌]]''，''<ref name="#3">{{Cite journal|title=Antimicrobial activity of flavonoids extracted from bergamot (Citrus bergamia Risso) peel, a byproduct of the essential oil industry|last=Mandalari|first=G.|last2=Bennett|first2=R. N.|date=2007-12-01|journal=Journal of Applied Microbiology|issue=6|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2672.2007.03456.x|volume=103|pages=2056–2064|issn=1364-5072|pmid=18045389|last3=Bisignano|first3=G.|last4=Trombetta|first4=D.|last5=Saija|first5=A.|last6=Faulds|first6=C. B.|last7=Gasson|first7=M. J.|last8=Narbad|first8=A.}}</ref>[[嗜酸乳桿菌|嗜酸乳杆菌]]，[[内氏放线菌|内氏放线菌]]，[[口服口状杆菌|口腔普雷沃菌]]<ref name="#3"/>[[嗜酸乳桿菌|嗜酸乳杆菌]]，[[黑色素丙酸杆菌|黑色素丙酸杆菌]]，[[普氏菌|牙龈卟啉单胞菌]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=In vitro antimicrobial activity of propolis samples from different geographical origins against certain oral pathogens|last=Koru|first=Ozgur|last2=Toksoy|first2=Fulya|date=2007-06-01|journal=Anaerobe|issue=3–4|doi=10.1016/j.anaerobe.2007.02.001|volume=13|pages=140–145|issn=1075-9964|pmid=17475517|last3=Acikel|first3=Cengiz Han|last4=Tunca|first4=Yasar Meric|last5=Baysallar|first5=Mehmet|last6=Uskudar Guclu|first6=Aylin|last7=Akca|first7=Eralp|last8=Ozkok Tuylu|first8=Asli|last9=Sorkun|first9=Kadriye}}</ref>以及[[白色念珠菌|白色念珠菌]]，[[熱帶念珠菌|热带]]和[[克柔念珠菌|克柔念珠菌]]等抗菌药物的证据。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Chemical compositions and antimicrobial activities of four different Anatolian propolis samples|last=Uzel|first=Ataç|last2=Sorkun|first2=Kadri˙ye|date=2005-04-25|journal=Microbiological Research|issue=2|doi=10.1016/j.micres.2005.01.002|volume=160|pages=189–195|pmid=15881836|last3=Önçağ|first3=Özant|last4=Çoğulu|first4=Dilşah|last5=Gençay|first5=Ömür|last6=Sali˙h|first6=Beki˙r}}</ref>尽管没有证明柚皮苷对微生物的[[脲酶|脲酶活]]性有任何抑制作用，但有证据证明其对[[幽門螺桿菌|幽门螺杆菌]]具有抗菌作用。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=In vitroAnti-Helicobacter pylori Activity of Some Flavonoids and Their Metabolites|last=Bae|first=Eun-Ah|last2=Han|first2=Myung|journal=Planta Medica|issue=5|doi=10.1055/s-2006-960805|year=1999|volume=65|pages=442–443|pmid=10454900|last3=Kim|first3=Dong-Hyun}}</ref>

柚皮素可以减少体外培养的HCV感染的[[肝細胞|肝细胞]]病毒的产生。这可能继发于柚皮素抑制[[極低密度脂蛋白|极低密度脂蛋白]]分泌的作用。 <ref name="pmid18393287">{{Cite journal|title=Apolipoprotein B-dependent hepatitis C virus secretion is inhibited by the grapefruit flavonoid naringenin|date=May 2008|journal=Hepatology|issue=5|doi=10.1002/hep.22197|volume=47|pages=1437–45|pmc=4500072|pmid=18393287}}</ref>柚皮苷的抗病毒作用目前正在临床研究中。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=A Pilot Study of the Grapefruit Flavonoid Naringenin for HCV Infection - Full Text View - ClinicalTrials.gov|url=http://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/show/NCT01091077?term=naringenin&rank=1|work=clinicaltrials.gov|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20101001003636/http://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/show/NCT01091077?term=naringenin&rank=1|archivedate=2010-10-01}}</ref>关于[[脊髓灰質炎病毒|脊髓灰质炎病毒]]， [[单纯疱疹病毒|HSV-1]]和[[单纯疱疹病毒|HSV-2]]的抗病毒作用的报道也已经发表，尽管病毒的复制并未受到抑制。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Inhibition of virus multiplication and alteration of cyclic AMP level in cell cultures by flavonoids|last=Mucsi|first=I.|last2=Prágai|first2=B. M.|date=1985-07-01|journal=Experientia|issue=7|doi=10.1007/BF01970018|volume=41|pages=930–931|language=en|issn=0014-4754|pmid=2989000}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Antiherpetic activities of flavonoids against herpes simplex virus type 1 (HSV-1) and type 2 (HSV-2)in vitro|last=Lyu|first=Su-Yun|last2=Rhim|first2=Jee-Young|date=2005-11-01|journal=Archives of Pharmacal Research|issue=11|doi=10.1007/BF02978215|volume=28|pages=1293–1301|language=en|issn=0253-6269|pmid=16350858|last3=Park|first3=Won-Bong}}</ref>

=== 抗炎 ===
