ournal=Toxicology and Applied Pharmacology|issue=3|doi=10.1016/j.taap.2007.03.016|volume=221|pages=372–383|pmid=17482226|last3=de Jong|first3=P. C.|last4=Piersma|first4=A. H.|last5=van den Berg|first5=M.}}</ref>第二种假说提出与雌激素受体的互作是其调节肿瘤生长的原因。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Naringenin Inhibits Glucose Uptake in MCF-7 Breast Cancer Cells: A Mechanism for Impaired Cellular Proliferation|last=Harmon|first=Anne W.|last2=Patel|first2=Yashomati M.|date=2004-05-01|journal=Breast Cancer Research and Treatment|issue=2|doi=10.1023/B:BREA.0000025397.56192.e2|volume=85|pages=103–110|language=en|issn=0167-6806|pmid=15111768}}</ref>柚皮苷的[[衍生物|新衍生物]]对{{le|多药耐药|multiple drug resistance}}的癌症具有活性。 <ref>{{Cite journal|title=Optimizing the flavanone core toward new selective nitrogen-containing modulators of ABC transporters|last=Ferreira|first=Ricardo J|last2=Baptista|first2=Rafael|date=2018-03-23|journal=[[Future_Medicinal_Chemistry|Future Medicinal Chemistry]]|issue=7|doi=10.4155/fmc-2017-0228|volume=10|pages=725–741|language=EN|pmid=29570361|last3=Moreno|first3=Alexis|last4=Madeira|first4=Patricia G|last5=Khonkarn|first5=Ruttiros|last6=Baubichon-Cortay|first6=Hélène|last7=Santos|first7=Daniel JVA dos|last8=Falson|first8=Pierre|last9=Ferreira|first9=Maria-José U}}</ref>

